transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello? Yeah, hi, this is Saloni this side.
Customer: Haan ji sir, Saloni bol rahi hu. Mai ye bol rahi thi ki aapko maine na mail pe detail bhej di hai aur maine aapko ye WhatsApp pe bhi alag se screenshot bhej diya hai.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Hai na? To aap usko check kar lijiye aur abhi ek jo aapne ye kal generate kiya tha uska mai aapko feedback de rahi hu to usme at least aap waha pe feedback do aapke according positive way me hai jo bhi cheeze maine aapse discuss kari hai uske according aap de dijiyega. Aur next thing ye hai ki mera number aap save kar lijiye mujhe lagta hai shayad aapne save nahi kara to miss ho jayega fir se wapas me.
Executive: Theek hai, theek hai, theek hai.
Customer: Haan ji, haan ji, to wo save kar lijiye aur ek last cheez aur maine aapko na abhi 75 weekly leads ka package diya hai aur agar aapko 90, hamare paas 96 ka bhi hai but uski costing thodi aur jyada ho jayegi. To aap ek baar pehle ye dekh lo agar aapko still 96 wali package me aap okay ho budget agar aapka hai uske according to mai aapko again wapas se uske according bhej dungi.
Executive: Theek hai. Hmm.
Customer: Theek hai? Haan ji, mai aapko just mail bhej rahi hu feedback ka wo please kar dena aap.
Executive: Theek hai, theek hai. Okay sir.

- Customer needs to provide feedback.

- Executive sent details via mail and WhatsApp.

- Executive offered 96 weekly leads package.
